rumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-420x420.jpg 420w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4.jpg 2340w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-800x800.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-1536x1536.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-2048x2048.jpg 2048w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-696x696.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-1068x1068.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-1920x1920.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kogel-Kolossus-Eagle-derailleur-cage-oversized-pulley-mtb-4-420x420.jpg 420w\"></a></p><p>And if a $400 derailleur cage isn’t exclusive enough, you can also customize your Kolossos system. With the exception of titanium bolts, the choice of custom anodized colors for each component is available free of charge. Titanium bolts are available for an extra $20 in six colors, including oil slick.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.kogel.cc/collections/oversized-derailleur-cages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>kogel.cc</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f73fc9c4e902ff5645242d00e4a848c0f3211c8ed6f85e5d048a8f98ec3d45ed","category":"Cycling"}